{"tid":306778,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[06:34] 朗尼：「C朗比我更強，只因為英超沒有美斯。」","createTime":"2017-07-02T21:39:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-09T22:25:21.000Z","uid":28938,"like":89,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"30c26c7d7ce4f2a23ac890c620de79d547cf0c95","tid":306778,"uid":28938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T21:39:58.000Z","msg":"<strong>[06:34] 朗尼：「C朗比我更強，只因為英超沒有美斯。」</strong><br />\n<br />\n曼聯隊長朗尼最近正於巴巴多斯中渡假，心情放鬆的他接受法國《Nineup》報訪問，期間談到C朗，一個曾經與他同一起點，現況卻截然不同的球星。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/03/052952_23433ed59fbd853b52a73d8afa22115b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F03%2F052952_23433ed59fbd853b52a73d8afa22115b.jpg&h=bea9d390&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n朗尼和C朗是曼聯的絕代雙驕，同於1985年出生，並肩帶領球會取得雙冠王。32歲的C朗自09年轉會皇馬後，入球量屢創新高，為球會贏得多次歐冠與西甲冠軍，去年更成功帶領葡萄牙勇奪歐國盃；另一邊，曾被譽為超級天才的朗尼，狀態卻連年下滑，去季淪為高薪後備，如今更淪落到沒有球會願意接收的地步。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/03/053108_2d0cdf4745cef08b5186d968542e8057.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F03%2F053108_2d0cdf4745cef08b5186d968542e8057.jpg&h=27f463ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n記者大膽地向朗尼展示他與C朗拿度的身型相片作比較，相片上的C.朗拿度一身肌肉，一看就知道受長年累月的苦練；但朗尼那張卻很難看到肌肉，雖然兩顆櫻桃甚為誘人，但贅肉卻更為明顯。如此直觀的對比，或許也揭示出了朗尼為何一直在走下坡路。<br />\n<br />\n朗尼放下照片，喝了一口生啤後向記者說：「十年前的我絕對比C朗更強，那時他只是個只懂盤扭的小伙子，我卻有著完美的身體與足球智慧，知道怎樣控制球賽和入球。」<br />\n<br />\n他接著道：「取得所有榮譽後我鬆懈了。C朗轉會後我缺乏了一個互相激勵的對象，逐漸喜愛夜生活，球隊訓練時也不投入；狀態也每下愈況。在差不多三十歲時，我在球場上已感到力不從心。」<br />\n<br />\n記者鼓勵著他還只是31歲，只要努力訓練重拾狀態，絕對可以尋找第二春。朗尼此時卻似乎已略有醉意，竟然用廣東話怒道：「屌！『春』你個頭咩！ C朗係西甲有美斯同佢鬥，英超個個廢柴，我踢咁好有鬼用咩？」<br />\n<br />\n朗尼說罷後更用酒瓶怒擲記者，記者落荒而逃，訪問中止。"},{"pid":"4e7b28046c8e141971b2629ddc2a23b26b893804","tid":306778,"uid":87646,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T21:44:15.000Z","msg":"ok! 睇到最後先知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d538ed071c5127b653bfacd799e96e227527317","tid":306778,"uid":17556,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T21:53:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<br />\n曼聯隊長朗尼最近正於巴巴多斯中渡假，心情放鬆的他接受<span style=\"color: red;\">法國《Nineup》報</span>訪問，期間談到C朗，一個曾經與他同一起點，現況卻截然不同的球星。<br />\n<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58873962d411151ea1770eb86185b35684faad08","tid":306778,"uid":13467,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T21:59:02.000Z","msg":"屌 我竟然睇哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7578bcc7338fa6cfc3b9c40a331b740ed3211ea","tid":306778,"uid":1790,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T22:00:48.000Z","msg":"雖然兩顆櫻桃甚為誘人<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6642022feaaf228bf4b454865d197c1177a9dab3","tid":306778,"uid":28938,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T22:56:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌 我竟然睇哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇哂有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cae64d043f65ba9e8002be4a9edec6132cc4bfb","tid":306778,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T23:11:06.000Z","msg":"假新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eba7578ed7eb7b781f2ad53141c4296785a39f9f","tid":306778,"uid":28938,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T23:14:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>假新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n邊忽假，合情合理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"021ca5eae717efc7ad19fcbb5560b1a88f230a5a","tid":306778,"uid":28938,